snippet.title: New Super Mario Bros. Wii: The Prankster Comets - NSMB. FMD Trailer
snippet.description:
Please read the pinned comment.

Original description:
Long time no see, huh?

I know I know, I said the mod would release before 2022 but I had some complications, remember that I'm doing all this for fun ^^
In the end I'm aiming for a Summer 2022 release, hope I'll be able to meet it

Thanks a lot to Rimea for including this trailer in the New Super Mario Bros. Franchise Modding Direct, find the link to the whole presentation here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvAH9bEEuPk

My discord: Asu-chan#2929
Check for updates of the mod on NHD: https://newerteam.com/nhd
